{{ infobox stadium |name =Barikadimy Stadium |image = |fullname = Barikadimy Stadium |location = [[Toamasina]], [[Madagascar]] |coordinates = {{coord|18|08|48.66|S|49|23|9.99|E|type:landmark|display=inline}} |built = |opened = |renovated = |expanded = |closed = |demolished = |owner = |operator = |surface = Grass |construction_cost = |architect = |general_contractor= |main_contractors = |former_names = |tenants = [[AS Fortior]] |capacity = 20,000 |dimensions = |scoreboard = }} '''Barikadimy Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Toamasina]], [[Madagascar]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. It hosts the home games of [[AS Fortior]] of the [[THB Champions League]]. The stadium has a capacity 20,000 spectators.<ref>http://www.worldstadiums.com/africa/countries/madagascar.shtml</ref>
