{{infobox football tournament | name = U-16 Turnier in Liechtenstein | logo = | caption = | founded = 2009 | abolished = 2009 | region = [[Liechtenstein]] ([[UEFA]]) | number of teams = 4 | current champions = {{flagicon|GER}} [[Germany national under-16 football team|Germany U-16]] | most titles = | most successful club = | most successful team = {{flagicon|GER}} [[Germany national under-16 football team|Germany U-16]] (1 title) | broadcasters = | motto = | website = | current = }} '''U-16 Tournament in Liechtenstein''' ({{lang-de|U-16 Turnier in Liechtenstein}}) is an [[association football]] friendly competition for junior national under-16 teams that took place in [[Eschen]] and [[Vaduz]], [[Liechtenstein]], in 2009.
The tournament was contested by 4 teams, with semifinals, third place match and final.
